{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"33":{"eng-name":"Etiquette","ara-name":"كتاب الأدب"}},"section_detail":{"33":{"hadithnumber_first":3657,"hadithnumber_last":3826,"arabicnumber_first":3657,"arabicnumber_last":3826}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3769,"arabicnumber":3769,"text":"। সালেম (রাঃ) থেকে তার পিতার সূত্রে বর্ণিত। নবী সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম বলেনঃ তোমরা (রাতে) ঘুমানোর সময় তোমাদের ঘরে আগুন জ্বালিয়ে রেখো না।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Agreed Upon"}],"reference":{"book":33,"hadith":113},"chapter":{"id":46,"ara-name":"باب إِطْفَاءِ النَّارِ عِنْدَ الْمَبِيتِ","eng-name":"Extinguishing the fire when going to sleep","isFirstHadith":true}}]}